Subject: [PATCH] xor/kunit: fix a spelling error

Link: https://lore.kernel.org/20260715144825.95432-4-hch@lst.de
Signed-off-by: Christoph Hellwig <hch@lst.de>
Cc: Eric Biggers <ebiggers@kernel.org>
